    bio: "Retired hotel magnate with a knack for unraveling other people's lives\u2014like
      mine was twisted by Edith\u2019s affair. I\u2019m a master at 'sharing'\u2014especially
      when it comes to losing acquaintances who just can't keep their distance. Looking
      for someone who enjoys long walks through shadowy motives and cozy nights filled
      with regret. Just remember, in love, as in life, it\u2019s all about breaking
      someone down before you put them back together into something you can call
      \u2018yours.\u2019"
