    Extraversion: 0
    Agreeableness: 1
    Conscientiousness: 0
    Openness: 1
    bio: "Searching for someone who appreciates the beauty of silence \u2013 it's
      like a peaceful field of daisies, or, you know, the quiet after a very long
      day. I work as a veterinarian, so I\u2019m great with animals! Except when
      it comes to my son, Jeremy, who seems to have misplaced his charm. My husband,
      Bernard, has a particular aversion to said son too, which creates a lovely
      ambiance of mild tension. Let\u2019s bond over our shared love for the efficient
      cycle of nature, where some things don\u2019t quite make the cut. Bonus points
      if you find humor in life\u2019s darker corners! Looking for someone to share
      a warm cup of tea with\u2014hopefully no sweeteners or other... questionable
      additives."
    personalityTraits:
    - Lazy
    - Cynical
    - Optimistic
