'
    DarkTriad: 
    HonestyHumility: 0
    Emotionality: 0
    Extraversion: 1
    Agreeableness: 0
    Conscientiousness: 0
    Openness: 0
    bio: "68 years of dodging life's little cuts, now I\u2019m just waiting for the
      right moment to slice back at Fred Christie, the butcher of my heart. My loved
      one was peeled away in the most unrefined manner; I much prefer clean separations.
      If you enjoy conversations laced with cynicism and the occasional morose musing
      on how sweet revenge can be, we might just hit it off\u2014but keep your skin
      at a safe distance. I work nights, and let\u2019s just say I know my way around
      a gas station, and it\u2019s not just the fuel I\u2019m interested in."
    personalityTraits:
    - Refined
    - Cynical
    - Rude
