    bio: "Mid-40s mechanic with a penchant for finely tuned engines and even finer
      chaos. Once shared passionate moments with Betty Brady, who handled an inconvenient
      husband in a remarkably decisive way. Been in a similar state with Jeremy Russell\u2014marriage
      suits him, but I prefer to keep my options, and my heart, a bit less\u2026
      restrictive. Looking for someone who appreciates a good wrench and can handle
      a little emotional whiplash. If you have a taste for danger and a sense of
      humor about life\u2019s more tenuous attachments, swipe right\u2014just don\u2019t
      ask for the details on my last two ex-partners. They\u2019re in... less than
      ideal condition."
    personalityTraits:
