    Emotionality: 1
    Extraversion: 0
    Agreeableness: 1
    Conscientiousness: 1
    Openness: 1
    bio: "Hi there! I'm a passionate hairdresser with a taste for rich, dark humor\u2014think
      of me as the stylist with a hint of vindictive charm. I\u2019m definitely not
      one to shy away from a good slice of the truth, especially when it comes to
      those who\u2019ve done me wrong, like Benjamin Simmons\u2014he\u2019s served
      me a terrible dish by taking my father off the menu. \nRecently, a petty appetizer
      had me eliminating my husband after a tantalizing affair with the irresistible
      Josephine Chikatilo. It\u2019s hard to swallow the guilt of it all, but let\u2019s
      just say the heart wants what it wants...even if it requires a little cutting
      here and there. \nIf you're into intricate hairstyles and even more intricate
      lives, let\u2019s bond over a bottle of red (blood?) wine! Wouldn\u2019t you
      just love to relish in the flavors of revenge together? \U0001F377"
    personalityTraits:
    - Dependent
